@startuml sequence-manajemen-staff-owner
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Manajemen Akun Staff (Owner)

actor Owner
participant "Aplikasi Web\n(Dashboard Owner)" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Lihat Daftar Staff ==

Owner -> App : Buka menu Manajemen Staff
App -> API : GET /internal/staff
API -> API : Verifikasi role = OWNER
API -> DB : SELECT staff WHERE role != OWNER\nOR role = STAFF
DB --> API : Daftar staff
API --> App : 200 OK + data
App --> Owner : Tampilkan daftar staff

== Tambah Staff ==

Owner -> App : Isi form staff\n(nama, email, password, status)
App -> API : POST /internal/staff
API -> API : Verifikasi role = OWNER
API -> DB : INSERT staff (role=STAFF, password_hash)
DB --> API : staff_id
API --> App : 201 Created
App --> Owner : Staff berhasil ditambahkan

== Edit & Reset Password ==

Owner -> App : Edit data staff
App -> API : PUT /internal/staff/{id}
API -> DB : UPDATE staff (nama, email, status)
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 200 OK
App --> Owner : Data staff diperbarui

Owner -> App : Reset password staff
App -> API : PATCH /internal/staff/{id}/reset-password
API -> DB : UPDATE password_hash
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 200 OK
App --> Owner : Password staff direset

== Nonaktifkan / Aktifkan ==

Owner -> App : Nonaktifkan akun staff
App -> API : PATCH /internal/staff/{id}/status\n{ status: NONAKTIF }
API -> DB : UPDATE staff.status = NONAKTIF
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 200 OK
App --> Owner : Staff dinonaktifkan

note over Owner, DB
  Owner tidak bisa dinonaktifkan
  oleh staff. Hanya owner yang
  mengelola akun staff.
end note

@enduml
